perun-slave-process-fs-project (3.1.4) stable; urgency=medium

  * Set permissions using setfacl and set group permissions as default.
  * It should improve user experience using project directories. New
    solution is more robust than using only sgid bit. Hence sgid bit is
    usually ignored by tools like rsync.

 -- Slavek Licehammer <slavek@ics.muni.cz>  Thu, 11 Aug 2016 17:04:09 +0200

